--- KEYCLOAK


### Credtentials B2B
# @no-log
POST {{kc_baseURL}}/realms/{{kc_Realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id=email-dispatch-gateway&
client_secret={{kc_B2B_localClientSecret}}&
grant_type=client_credentials

> {% client.global.set("kc_B2B_accessToken", response.body["access_token"]) %}


### Credtentials B2C
# @no-log
POST {{kc_baseURL}}/realms/{{kc_Realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id=email-dispatch-gateway-users&
username={{kc_B2C_localUsername}}&
password={{lc_B2C_localPassword}}&
grant_type=password

> {% client.global.set("kc_B2C_accessToken", response.body["access_token"]) %}
